### G4 - Consultas — API Externa
### Compatível com o HTTP Client do IntelliJ/WebStorm e a extensão REST Client (VS Code).
### Preencha @apiKey com uma chave gerada no G4 (Admin -> API Keys).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = cole_sua_chave_aqui
@patientId = p1

### 1) Histórico de consultas realizadas do paciente (somente status=completed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/external/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/consultations/history
Authorization: ApiKey {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 2) Listar consultas (filtros opcionais: status, patientId, startDate, endDate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/external/v1/consultations?status=completed
Authorization: ApiKey {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 2b) Listar com o header alternativo X-API-Key (em vez de Authorization)
GET {{baseUrl}}/external/v1/consultations?patientId={{patientId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 3) Buscar consulta por ID (troque <id> por um id real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/external/v1/consultations/<id>
Authorization: ApiKey {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 4) Sem chave -> deve retornar 401 (demonstra a proteção)
GET {{baseUrl}}/external/v1/consultations
Accept: application/json
